{"tid":1800582,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"黨鐵未來更換支援電子支付之閘機  由中國公司中標","createTime":"2019-12-28T03:28:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-30T09:15:10.000Z","uid":41818,"like":5,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"0e7f48c427d4ffc7c6bb5974773bb753f99035f6","tid":1800582,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T03:28:06.000Z","msg":"點解 #火車未到站 ？因為車站需要更換支援電子支付嘅閘機，而中標嘅係中国公司<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n響車站「被裝修」之前，鐵路公司已計劃更換閘機同售票機。最近有中国公司搶閘發出「中標公告」，宣布以4.41億港元投得更換閘機及售票機嘅合約。<br />\n<br />\n上海華銘智能終端設備股份有限公司 於12月19日發出公告，指「收到香港鐵路有限公司發出的中標通知書，確定華銘智能（聯合體成員） 與香港的高明科技工程有限公司（聯合體牽頭人）組成的聯合體為&ldquo;更換及更新自動收費系統設備（閘機、售票機）（項目編號：C3025-18E）&rdquo;的中標單位」。（傳送門： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2sQaKZY\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2sQaKZY&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPG58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=232d261d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2sQaKZY</a> ）<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，鐵路公司於2018年中曾就更換閘機及售票機進行招標：更換約1500部閘機及420部售票機，翻新和升級約500部閘機，並提升約240部閘機、100部售票機和16部自助客務機，以支援各種電子支付服務，包括QR Code、非接觸式信用卡及手機NFC支付等。（合約資格預審中之描述： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2rnhpuk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2rnhpuk&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPG58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=6ca27159\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2rnhpuk</a> ）<br />\n<br />\n高明科技對站長或其他鐵路人而言並不陌生，皆因佢唔少業務與自動收費系統有關。至於上海华铭智能又係乜水？參考其網頁，呢間公司負責生產中國不少地鐵系統嘅閘機及售票機，當中包括港鐵有份參與、由京港地鐵營運嘅北京地鐵大興綫（<a href=\"http://bit.ly/376lXVf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F376lXVf&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPG58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=49e0879e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/376lXVf</a> ）；至於海外案例則有印度及馬來西亞。<br />\n<br />\n更換支援電子支付嘅自動收費系統乃大勢所趨，鐵路公司早前宣布於2020年中提供「二維碼付費乘車」服務，正式推出後首12個月只獨家支援AlipayHK（支付寶香港），隨後則開放予其他服務提供者（包括WeChat Pay、TNG 以及銀聯）。（見港鐵2018年新聞稿： <a href=\"http://bit.ly/2Sjcplm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Sjcplm&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPG58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=fef05edd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2Sjcplm</a> ）<br />\n<br />\n對鐘意用電子錢包嘅乘客而言，開放更多支付方式或許帶來便利，甚至享受各種優惠。但呢啲「便利」與「優惠」，使用者又要唔要付出任何代價？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/train.not.arriving/photos/a.1695222363852185/3303726426335096/?type=1&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftrain.not.arriving%2Fphotos%2Fa.1695222363852185%2F3303726426335096%2F%3Ftype%3D1%26theater&d=CRZj9ITMXIzKHLmvffUzPG58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=7c268a92\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/train.not.arriving/photos/a.1695222363852185/3303726426335096/?type=1&amp;theater</a>"},{"pid":"81193d18595f553011f25b62ead24e0040acedab","tid":1800582,"uid":272531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T03:34:41.000Z","msg":"「黃色經濟圈」認證要大家幫手 - 籌款箱計劃<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1800571\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1800571</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"e55c4564f9cb6322d1f984035063c68f02357603","tid":1800582,"uid":105298,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T03:40:38.000Z","msg":"明明八達通仲方便，<br />\n一係轉用visa同master卡<br />\n轉乜撚支那寶，想裝一拆十<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cb2b07c5a31027799114297357f9e0900a2a8a6","tid":1800582,"uid":73054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T03:42:29.000Z","msg":"支那公司NFC<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab64bab65d3ce027b2507d372839edcf6ec69130","tid":1800582,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e55c4564f9cb6322d1f984035063c68f02357603","tid":1800582,"uid":105298,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-12-28T03:40:38.000Z","msg":"明明八達通仲方便，<br />\n一係轉用visa同master卡<br />\n轉乜撚支那寶，想裝一拆十<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgm